    <item>
      <title>January</title>
      <link>https://diary2.duoyu.ren/2023/01/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Jan 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://diary2.duoyu.ren/2023/01/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;有朋自遠&#34;&gt;有朋自遠&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;It is with great pleasure that I begin to &lt;strong&gt;pen these memoirs&lt;/strong&gt;, reflecting upon the many fascinating experiences and adventures &lt;em&gt;that have shaped my life&lt;/em&gt;. As I cast my mind back to a recent day in Shanghai, I recall the many challenges and delights that it held.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The day began at the crack of dawn, as I set my sights on mastering the intricacies of the German language. With diligent study and practice, I made significant progress, pushing the boundaries of my knowledge and understanding.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>January</title>
      <link>https://diary2.duoyu.ren/2024/01/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Jan 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://diary2.duoyu.ren/2024/01/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;網絡衝浪，形同裸泳，焉有隱私可言？碎念無益無害，不如輯錄在此。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;以下測試樣式：我想让你扮演一个专业英语翻译员，拼写检查员以及语法改进专家，我可能和你说任何语言，你需要识别我说的语言，并且翻译为正确和改进为英语版本，如果我说的是英语，我想让你用更优美的简洁和更高级的词汇和句子去替换我A0-level的词汇和句子，并且保证句意不变，并且要书面一点，你只需要回复你修改后的结果，不需要回复任何解释和其他内容，我的第一句话是&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>January</title>
